-- Airbus says Hong Kong Aviation to buy 60 planes
-- 
-- Thu Jun 20, 2013 4:41am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/06/20/us-air-show-hkac-airbus-idUSBRE95J08D20130620

 

 PARIS  (Reuters) - Hong Kong Aviation Capital signed a memorandum of understanding at the Paris Airshow on Thursday to buy 40 Airbus ( EAD.PA ) A320neo and 20 A321neo aircraft. 
 The deal is worth $6.4 billion at list prices. (Reporting by  Tim Hepher ; Editing by  James Regan )